				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				OK, everyone, a couple of things.<BR>
1. Anyone can fletch<BR>
2. Fletching is expensive so be prepared to invest heavily, although it can start to make you a tidy profit once you're in the higher lvls.<BR>
3. The Trueshot Longbow can be made by anyone, but it can only be used by a ranger<BR>
4. There used to be a beautiful fletching site listed in EQLinks, however it is not listed anymore.<BR>
<BR>
Fortunately, I printed hard copies of everything listed on that site. Due to the growing number of fletchers, I have decided to put all of this information on my website. Keep checking back from time to time for my website URL. Until then feel free to hail me in game or send me an e-mail for any questions, if I am not busy in game i will answer all I can.<BR>
<BR>
Torlaor<BR>
Barbarian Warrior of 16 Winters<BR>
Newly Appointed Master Fletcher (102)<BR>
Successful Builder of a Trueshot Longbow<BR>
Erollisi Marr Server<BR>
thirish1@hotmail.com<BR>
(put &quot;Fletching Question&quot; in the subject of your e-mails)
